                                Didukung oleh para ahli coating berpengalaman.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <!-- Card 5: Penerbitan Cepat -->
                    <div class="col-12 col-sm-6 col-lg">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-4 p-4 h-100 text-center shadow-sm" style="border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; min-height: 200px;">
                            <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded-circle mx-auto mb-4" style="width: 64px; height: 64px; background: rgba(30, 58, 95, 0.1);">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" fill="#1e3a5f" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path d="M5.52.359A.5.5 0 0 1 6 0h4a.5.5 0 0 1 .474.658L8.694 6H12.5a.5.5 0 0 1 .395.807l-7 9a.5.5 0 0 1-.873-.454L6.823 9.5H3.5a.5.5 0 0 1-.48-.641l2.5-8.5z"/>
